high_descs: Move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Bring the fork to the table.
Put the fork in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug on the table.
Bring the mug to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the wall, then turn right and head to the coffee machine on the far counter.
Pick the fork near the potato.
Go right then around the island, then face the island so the chair is to your left.
Put the fork with the tines upward in the cup in between the fork and the knife on the table.
Take the cup from the table.
Turn right and go in front of the sink.
Put the cup to the right of the kettle in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, move past the door to the wall, then turn right and move past the stove and oven to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the fork on the counter to the right of the beige coffee maker and to the left of the sink.
Turn right and move past the refrigerator then turn right and face the corner of the kitchen island next to the black chair.
Place the fork in the gray cup in the center of the kitchen island to the left of the knife and to the right of the fork.
Pick up the cup containing the fork from the kitchen island.
Turn right, move past the refrigerator, then turn left and move towards and face the sink.
Place the cup containing the fork in the sink between the spatula and the silver tea kettle.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup containing a fork in the sink.
